    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/9ad80540cc89f2c706161d7d4b3f3697.avif?t=1758102174\" width=940 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/b6decf2c521e17972518211a0ddf3adf.poster.avif?t=1758102174\" width=780 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/b6decf2c521e17972518211a0ddf3adf.webm?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/b6decf2c521e17972518211a0ddf3adf.mp4?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组成原力融合阵型，爆发强力攻击</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原力之间相互贯通、能够彼此转化。若想打出最强一击，必须让主攻单位与其他原力类型的单位协同作战，构建原力融合阵。阵型越稀有、搭配越巧妙，其爆发的威力就越强大！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/252a39b52672845f18c360d204a70fe3.avif?t=1758102174\" width=940 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/d4f446849b1ff8ef8d520909cd03a1b8.poster.avif?t=1758102174\" width=780 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/d4f446849b1ff8ef8d520909cd03a1b8.webm?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/d4f446849b1ff8ef8d520909cd03a1b8.mp4?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>让蘑菇合体进化，解锁强大的技能</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两个同等级、同原力的菇菇战士可以合体，进化成为更高阶的守护者。每晋升一个等级，菇菇骑士就可以解锁一项新技能。每一个菇菇宝宝最终都可以成长为强大的菇菇骑士！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/de2b51a32fdc647c3b320e89114b4295.avif?t=1758102174\" width=940 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/38434007b43c2f8cdd79d5dfff869840.poster.avif?t=1758102174\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/38434007b43c2f8cdd79d5dfff869840.webm?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/38434007b43c2f8cdd79d5dfff869840.mp4?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>编辑基因，打造超级英雄或者完美团队</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在进化过程中，你可以选择以何种方式继承原始两个低阶单位的基因链条（技能）。通过合理取舍与搭配，创造独一无二的超级菇菇英雄，或亲密无间的强力战术阵容！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/4a241b14221ed2cbe477830333ec21f1.avif?t=1758102174\" width=940 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/fc49968633a2067e9fdc3e7149955a34.poster.avif?t=1758102174\" width=780 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/fc49968633a2067e9fdc3e7149955a34.webm?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/fc49968633a2067e9fdc3e7149955a34.mp4?t=1758102174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的构筑元素，打造每一次独特的体验</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>上百种独特角色，搭配多样化的敌人、遗物、权杖与建筑，共同营造出一场充满未知与惊喜的Roguelike旅程！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015030/extras/5b08b84a6f1a8402535b64f7cf5e956e.avif?t=1758102174\" width=940 height=184 /></span></p>",
